<h3 id="cable-management-in-a-600-gaming-pc">Cable Management in a $600 Gaming PC</h3>

<p>Proper cable management is a must, regardless of your experience in the world of PC building.</p>

<p>Whether youâ€™re building in a small micro ATX case or a full tower case, youâ€™re going to want to wire up your rig properly.</p>

